{"tid":2411562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長實102.8億奪啟德住宅地","createTime":"2021-02-17T11:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T03:24:02.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cef5a7759b2200d483d7c0a80167c1ae1695b04","tid":2411562,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"班連登仔話長實撤資香港，而家繼續買地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>地政總署公布，啟德跑道區最後一幅住宅地皮由長實以102.8億元奪得，每呎樓面地價約15,861元，屬於市場估值預期內，並貼近估值上限，但較中國海外等在2019年11月投得的毗鄰地皮（第4A區2號）每呎地價13,238元，則高出近2成。值得留意的是，是次為長實首次奪得啟德地皮。<br />\n<br />\n長實發言人回應指，對在牛年伊始投得啟德跑道區最後一幅住宅地皮感到欣喜，並形容地皮條件優越，是罕有的市區海景地皮，是唯一一塊單邊的地皮臨近維港景緻及毗鄰未來都會公園，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">會將致力發展高質素的市中心海景豪宅項目，並且強調對香港未來經濟充滿信心。</span></span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2879508/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%AE%E9%96%8B%E6%A8%99%E3%80%91%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6102.8%E5%84%84%E5%A5%AA%E5%95%9F%E5%BE%B7%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%9C%B0%20%E5%91%8E%E5%83%B915861%E5%85%83%20%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%85%85%E6%BB%BF%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83?mtc=60007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2879508%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259A%25AE%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A8%2599%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6102.8%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%2585%25E5%259C%25B0%2520%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B915861%25E5%2585%2583%2520%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2595%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2585%2585%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BF%2583%3Fmtc%3D60007&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2yrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=fb1af7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2879508/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%AE%E9%96%8B%E6%A8